 HmC-Ygir6ZNrYthTBYE221UOFJPS1ZFTU1KSkZaVVhFNFA2S01XMFg2RS4u&route=shorturl
 \n\nHosted by The Mad Studies Hub
  (https://www.yorku.ca/research/madstudieshub/)\n\nThis event brings
  together community\, organisers\, researchers\, and students to discuss
  the intersections between mental health\, homelessness\, and police
  abolition on-and-off York University campus. Food and refreshments will
  be available! Please bring any new\, or gently used\, clean sleping
  bags\, tents\, tarps\, backpacks\, or sealed hygiene products.
