SUMMARY:Road Salt Alternatives Webinar - by Ontario Salt Pollution
  Coalition
LOCATION:Virtual
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://www.waterwatchers.ca/road_salt_alternatives\n\nHosted by Ontario
  Salt Pollution Coalition (https://saltcoalition.ca/)\n\nWhile there's
  scientific & civic consensus that road salt is a huge issue for our
  environmental systems\, conflicting information abounds when it comes to
  salt alternatives. Join this webinar to sort through the realities\,
  myths\, and mysteries of alternatives to road salt and what you can do to
  help.
END:VEVENT
