SUMMARY:Civic Meetup - How is your local councillor voting on climate? - by
  Civic Tech Toronto
LOCATION:Hybrid
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://guild.host/events/civic-meetup-532-how-gha2ar\n\nHosted by Civic
  Tech Toronto (https://civictech.ca/)\n\nCivic Tech Toronto's weekly
  meetups bring together Torontonians who want to improve the city through
  design\, tech\, and data. A groups of researchers at ClimateFast have
  documented and analyzed every single climate-related voting records of
  City of Toronto councillors since 2018 to present. Come hear abotu the
  results! Followed by project breakout sessions.
END:VEVENT
